═══════════════════════════════════════════
ERROR HANDLING
═══════════════════════════════════════════

AI calls:
  - 3 retries, exponential backoff: 2s → 4s → 8s
  - On JSON parse failure: append to prompt:
    "Your last response was not valid JSON. Reply with ONLY
     valid JSON starting with { or [. Nothing else."
    Then retry.
  - Strip markdown fences before every JSON parse:
    text.strip().lstrip("```json").lstrip("```").rstrip("```").strip()
  - Gemini-specific: handle SAFETY block responses gracefully
  - Groq-specific: handle rate limit (429) with longer backoff

File operations:
  - PDF: handle fitz exceptions, empty files, password protection
  - JSON: handle malformed data with defaults
  - Always validate Pydantic model — never trust raw dicts

